 5 Ways to Instantly Appear More Confident 
 
 
By  Steve    255 
 

 
 
 
 
 Today I’m going to teach how you to appear more confident. 
 Why?  Because confidence is one of the most important skills in life that you can acquire (other than learning to  use the Force , obviously). 
 Now, I’m not teaching you this stuff just so you can become some sleazy pickup artist.  I’m teaching you because I know how important even a little bit of confidence can be in everyday situations, whether it’s negotiating with your boss for a raise, buying a car, giving a presentation, or meetin